<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>管理后台 - <%= settings.title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free@5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        :root {
            --primary: #667eea;
            --primary-dark: #764ba2;
            --sidebar-bg: #2c3e50;
            --sidebar-text: #ecf0f1;
            --content-bg: #f5f7fa;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: var(--content-bg);
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            background: var(--sidebar-bg);
            color: var(--sidebar-text);
            padding: 20px 0;
            position: fixed;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        
        .sidebar-header {
            padding: 0 20px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .sidebar-header h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; }
        .sidebar-header p { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.7; }
        
        .nav-menu { list-style: none; }
        
        .nav-menu li a {
            display: block;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            color: var(--sidebar-text);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .nav-menu li a:hover,
        .nav-menu li a.active {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
        }
        
        .nav-menu li a i { margin-right: 10px; width: 20px; }
        
        .main-content {
            margin-left: 250px;
            flex: 1;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        
        .page-header { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .page-header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; color: #333; }
        .page-header p { color: #666; margin-top: 5px; }
        
        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .card-header h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #333; }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .stat-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .stat-card i { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .stat-card .stat-number { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; }
        .stat-card .stat-label { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; }
        
        .data-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        
        .data-table th,
        .data-table td {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .data-table th {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .data-table tr:hover { background: #f8f9fa; }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

        .btn-danger { background: #e74c3c; color: white; }
        .btn-success { background: #27ae60; color: white; }
        .btn-warning { background: #f39c12; color: white; }
        .btn-info { background: #3498db; color: white; }
        .btn-secondary { background: #7f8c8d; color: white; }

        .btn-sm { padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 12px; }

        /* Alert 样式 */
        .alert {
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .alert-success { background: #d4edda; color: #155724; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; }
        .alert-danger { background: #f8d7da; color: #721c24; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; }
        .alert-warning { background: #fff3cd; color: #856404; border: 1px solid #ffeeba; }
        .alert-info { background: #d1ecf1; color: #0c5460; border: 1px solid #bee5eb; }
        
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 500; color: #333; }
        
        .form-group input,
        .form-group select,
        .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group select:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .message {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message.success { background: #d4edda; color: #155724; }
        .message.error { background: #f8d7da; color: #721c24; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-header">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-bookmark"></i> MyNav</h2>
            <p>管理后台</p>
        </div>
        
        <ul class="nav-menu">
            <li><a href="/admin" class="<%= action === 'dashboard' ? 'active' : '' %>"><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> <span>仪表盘</span></a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/category" class="<%= action === 'category' ? 'active' : '' %>"><i class="fas fa-folder"></i> <span>分类管理</span></a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/link" class="<%= action === 'link' ? 'active' : '' %>"><i class="fas fa-link"></i> <span>链接管理</span></a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/settings" class="<%= action === 'settings' ? 'active' : '' %>"><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> <span>系统设置</span></a></li>
            <li><a href="/" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> <span>访问首页</span></a></li>
            <li><a href="/logout"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> <span>退出登录</span></a></li>
        </ul>
    </aside>
    
    <main class="main-content">
        <% if (action === 'dashboard') { %>
            <div class="page-header">
                <h1><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> 仪表盘</h1>
                <p>欢迎回来，管理员</p>
            </div>

            <% if (message) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-success"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <%= message %></div>
            <% } %>
            <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-danger"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> <%= error %></div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-folder"></i>
                    <div class="stat-number"><%= stats.categories %></div>
                    <div class="stat-label">分类数量</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
                    <div class="stat-number"><%= stats.links %></div>
                    <div class="stat-label">链接总数</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    <div class="stat-number"><%= stats.todayLinks %></div>
                    <div class="stat-label">今日新增</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        <% } else if (action === 'category') { %>
            <div class="page-header">
                <h1><i class="fas fa-folder"></i> 分类管理</h1>
                <p>管理书签分类</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header"><h3>添加分类</h3></div>
                <form method="POST" action="/admin/category/add">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>分类名称</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="输入分类名称">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>父分类</label>
                        <select name="fid">
                            <option value="0">作为一级分类</option>
                            <% categories.forEach(function(cat) { %>
                                <% if (cat.fid === 0) { %>
                                    <option value="<%= cat.id %>">-- <%= cat.name %></option>
                                <% } %>
                            <% }); %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>权重 (越大越靠前)</label>
                        <input type="number" name="weight" value="100">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>图标 (FontAwesome)</label>
                        <input type="text" name="font_icon" value="fa-folder" placeholder="例如: fa-star">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">添加分类</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header"><h3>分类列表</h3></div>
                <table class="data-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr><th>ID</th><th>名称</th><th>类型</th><th>显示</th><th>权重</th><th>操作</th></tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% categories.forEach(function(cat) { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td><%= cat.id %></td>
                                <td><i class="fas <%= cat.font_icon %>"></i> <%= cat.name %></td>
                                <td><%= cat.fid === 0 ? '一级分类' : '二级分类' %></td>
                                <td>
                                    <% if (cat.hidden == 1) { %>
                                        <span style="color: #999;">隐藏</span>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        <span style="color: green;">显示</span>
                                    <% } %>
                                </td>
                                <td><%= cat.weight %></td>
                                <td>
                                    <form method="POST" action="/admin/category/toggle" style="display: inline;">
                                        <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= cat.id %>">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm"><%= cat.hidden == 1 ? '显示' : '隐藏' %></button>
                                    </form>
                                    <form method="POST" action="/admin/category/delete" style="display: inline;" onsubmit="return confirm('确定删除？')">
                                        <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= cat.id %>">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">删除</button>
                                    </form>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        <% }); %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            
        <% } else if (action === 'link') { %>
            <div class="page-header">
                <h1><i class="fas fa-link"></i> 链接管理</h1>
                <p>管理书签链接</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header"><h3>添加链接</h3></div>
                <form method="POST" action="/admin/link/add">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>链接标题</label>
                        <input type="text" name="title" required placeholder="输入链接标题">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>链接地址</label>
                        <input type="url" name="url" required placeholder="https://example.com">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>描述</label>
                        <textarea name="description" rows="2" placeholder="简短描述"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>所属分类</label>
                        <select name="fid" required>
                            <% categories.forEach(function(cat) { %>
                                <option value="<%= cat.id %>"><%= cat.fid === 0 ? '' : '└─ ' %><%= cat.name %></option>
                            <% }); %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>权重</label>
                        <input type="number" name="weight" value="100">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">添加链接</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header"><h3>链接列表</h3></div>
                <table class="data-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr><th>标题</th><th>URL</th><th>分类</th><th>置顶</th><th>操作</th></tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% links.forEach(function(link) { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td><%= link.title %></td>
                                <td><a href="<%= link.url %>" target="_blank"><%= link.url.substring(0, 40) %></a></td>
                                <td><%= link.fid %></td>
                                <td><%= link.topping ? '是' : '否' %></td>
                                <td>
                                    <form method="POST" action="/admin/link/toggle-top" style="display: inline;">
                                        <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= link.id %>">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm"><%= link.topping ? '取消置顶' : '置顶' %></button>
                                    </form>
                                    <form method="POST" action="/admin/link/delete" style="display: inline;" onsubmit="return confirm('确定删除？')">
                                        <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= link.id %>">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">删除</button>
                                    </form>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        <% }); %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            
        <% } else if (action === 'settings') { %>
            <div class="page-header">
                <h1><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> 系统设置</h1>
                <p>配置网站基本信息</p>
            </div>

            <% if (message) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-success"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <%= message %></div>
            <% } %>
            <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-danger"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> <%= error %></div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="card">
                <form method="POST" action="/admin/settings">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>网站标题</label>
                        <input type="text" name="title" value="<%= settings.title %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>副标题</label>
                        <input type="text" name="subtitle" value="<%= settings.subtitle %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>网站描述</label>
                        <textarea name="description" rows="3"><%= settings.description %></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>关键词</label>
                        <input type="text" name="keywords" value="<%= settings.keywords %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>每分类显示链接数</label>
                        <input type="number" name="link_num" value="<%= settings.link_num %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>默认主题</label>
                        <select name="theme" class="form-control">
                            <option value="1" <%= settings.theme === '1' || !settings.theme ? 'selected' : '' %>>主题1 - WebStack风格（左侧导航）</option>
                            <option value="2" <%= settings.theme === '2' ? 'selected' : '' %>>主题2 - 深色居中（多引擎搜索）</option>
                            <option value="3" <%= settings.theme === '3' ? 'selected' : '' %>>主题3 - 卡片风格（固定导航栏）</option>
                        </select>
                        <small class="form-text text-muted">选择网站首页默认显示的主题风格</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>自定义 Header</label>
                        <textarea name="custom_header" rows="5" placeholder="可放置统计代码、自定义CSS样式或JavaScript代码"><%= settings.custom_header || '' %></textarea>
                        <small class="form-text text-muted">插入到页面 &lt;head&gt; 标签内，用于添加统计代码、自定义样式等</small>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">保存设置</button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="card" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-exchange-alt"></i> 书签导入/导出</h3>
                <p>支持浏览器书签格式（HTML）导入导出</p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 15px;">
                    <a href="/admin/export" class="btn btn-success"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> 导出书签</a>
                    <form method="POST" action="/admin/import" enctype="multipart/form-data" style="display: inline;">
                        <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
                            <input type="file" name="bookmarks" accept=".html" style="display: none;" id="importFile" onchange="this.form.submit()">
                            <label for="importFile" class="btn btn-warning"><i class="fas fa-upload"></i> 导入书签</label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-database"></i> 数据备份/恢复</h3>
                <p>备份包含所有分类、链接、设置和用户数据（JSON格式）</p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 15px;">
                    <a href="/admin/backup" class="btn btn-info"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> 下载备份</a>
                    <form method="POST" action="/admin/restore" enctype="multipart/form-data" style="display: inline;">
                        <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
                            <input type="file" name="backup" accept=".json" style="display: none;" id="restoreFile" onchange="if(confirm('恢复数据将覆盖现有数据，确定要继续吗？')) this.form.submit()">
                            <label for="restoreFile" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-upload"></i> 恢复数据</label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="alert alert-warning" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> <strong>注意：</strong>恢复数据会覆盖现有数据，请谨慎操作！
                </div>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
